# Architecture boundaries

- Component boundary changes require an ADR.
- Data model, public API, auth behavior, deployment topology, persistence, event schema, external dependencies, and security model changes require an ADR.
- Avoid broad refactors inside feature slices.
- Prefer boring, standard patterns over novel abstractions.
